name: Onspel
description:
Onspel

Enjoy getting lost and wandering the strange world of Allfield on the little island of Onspel. Enjoy the views, and the more you explore, the more secrets and mysteries you will uncover.

  • WASD controls
  • Mouse: Look/Aim
  • Space: Jump
  • E: Interact
  • I: Inventory Menu/Save/Load
  • C: Card Menu
  • G: Garden Menu
  • T: Torch (with fire kit)
  • F: Campfire (with fire kit)
